## Entry point

- Read `AGENTS.md` first and follow its **load order**.
- Treat tracked docs as the **source of truth**; chat history is not authoritative.

## Context hygiene (required)

- Prefer generating focused briefs only from the dogfood test fixture when validating fixture behavior: `specy-road brief <NODE_ID> -o work/brief-<NODE_ID>.md --repo-root tests/fixtures/specy_road_dogfood` (equivalent script: `specy_road/bundled_scripts/generate_brief.py`; there is no top-level `scripts/` directory — see `.cursor/rules/020-change-discipline.mdc`).
- Don’t load or edit large unrelated areas of the repo.

